fields.name: Helmet
fields.description: Cricket helmet for batsmen, Weighs approximatley 940 Gms. including a new improved fixed grill for increased safety. Increased facial & side protection. Removable and washable sweatband. Confirms to Latest ICC/BS 2013 safety standards including the back extention for more safety.

fields.name: Cricket Bat
fields.description: With an aggressive powerful profile and smouldering black graphics the Shadow is the ideal choice for the player who likes to make thing happen on the field. The addition of the new ‘Counterbalance’ handle enhances the ‘pick up’ to provide a bat which packs a heavyweight punch.

fields.name: Cricket Top
fields.description: A fantastically strong shirt that will stand up to the rigours of the cricket season. The Matrix shirt is as breathable as possible, ensuring cricketers young and old will keep cool even in the hottest conditions. In the modern game, with players become increasingly athletic and moving more dynamically, it was crucial that all Gray Nicolls cricket shirts were ergonomically designed.

fields.name: Cricket Bottom
fields.description: Professional quality garment. Moisture management and wicking materials with airflow to keep players cool. A supportive rib material which is used for the yoke and back panel of the leg give these trousers a modern, comfortable fit. Supplied with ivory trim only.

fields.name: Cricket Cap
fields.description: Designed to fit all head sizes, we've made the Melton Cap with an elasticated headband that gives the user a secure and comfortable fit, giving you peace of mind when are diving for the ball.

fields.name: Cricket Box
fields.description: Masuri Jockstrap with box is designed to hold the protective box to place under the whites and leave you to focus on more important things at the crease.

fields.name: Football Top
fields.description: Puma short sleeve training top with dry cell technology, Printed branding. 100% polyester. Crew neck. Straight hem.

fields.name: Football
fields.description: Emulate your heroes on the pitch with this Nike Strike Premier League Football which is ready for everyday play and features a high-contrast graphic design which allows you to track the the ball with ease. The ball has Nike Aerowtrac grooves which delivers an accurate ball flight right off the foot, whilst the textured casing helps enhance control and the balls 12-panels are machine stitched for long-lasting durability.

fields.name: Tennis Racket
fields.description: The Ultra Power Pro 105 delivers a nice boost of power and stability for recreational tennis players. Innovative frame and shaft constructions create thicker geometries that help stabilize the frame during the swing, while its relatively light weight and midplus head find an impactful balance of comfort and forgiveness. Featuring design and performance inspired by the performance Ultra series, the Ultra Power Pro 105 caters to a wide variety of ages and styles.

fields.name: Tennis Top
fields.description: This Mens adidas Fab Polo Shirt has been crafted with Climalite technology that wick sweat away from the skin to keep you feeling dry teamed with a lightweight and breathable design along with a three button placket and short sleeves for a comfortable fit.

fields.name: Stumps with Bails
fields.description: Made From Finest Quality Hardwood. Spring Return Stumps are natural wooden stumps with strong cast iron base and heavy duty spring return mechanism.

fields.name: White Cricket Ball
fields.description: Hand stitched 4-piece construction with 4 Layer quilted centre, Waxed and finished to English requirements, selected hide cover

fields.name: Cricket Gloves
fields.description: The Libro batting glove offers the highest levels of protection and comfort. Fully articulated with aptimum ventilation in palm areas.

fields.name: Cricket Thigh Gaurd
fields.description: Contoured thigh guard with extra large inner thigh pad creates an all in one lower body protection system. Combination of high density foam for lightweight, high impact protection, Adjustable elastic straps ensure a custom and comfortable fit

fields.name: Cricket Arm Gaurd
fields.description: The Arm Guard will absorb impact and stave off what would potentially be painful blows. The Premium PU Cover ensures the durability of the arm guard while maintaining its lightweight performance. The arm guard's towel backing works hard to absorb all moisture that can be generated when batting for long periods under intense pressure. Fitted with a stretchy strap, the arm guard is fully adjustable for a comfortable fit.

fields.name: Cricket Bag
fields.description: The main storage compartment is big enough to fit in the vast majority of your playing kit, essential for someone that has a lot of gear. Your pads and gloves will fit comfortably in here, with all your other internal protection. There’s an internal bat storage sleeve to keep your pride and joy as protected as possible.

fields.name: Batting Pads
fields.description: The tri-system vertical shin bolster offers fantastic coverage across the lower leg, where full, fast deliveries can have serious impact. The HD foam and cane rod combination give great coverage across the front of the batting pad, with lightweight protection which will never compromise your performance or speed across the ground. Again, this batting pad protection is supremely lightweight, with no impact on movement.

fields.name: Wickets Keeping Gloves
fields.description: The Prestige WicketKeeping gloves are a high class, high-performance glove that has been designed and refined by our product team in Robertsbridge. Sitting within the Classic range, the Prestige ooze class with their predominantly white colourway.
